    "Focal Tversky loss modifies the Tversky loss by adding the focal parameters.",
    "The Combo loss is an example of compound loss, which sums up the Dice and cross-entropy loss.",
    "Since a review of loss functions is beyond the scope of this paper, we refer to the detailed review article 72.",
    "We follow the metrics often used in semantic segmentation to evaluate the models' performance.",
    "Precision is the portion of correctly identified damage (TP) among all predicted damage (TP+FP), while recall is the portion of correctly identified damage (TP) among all actual damages (TP+FN)."
